<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">The Seven Songs of Merlin is the second book in a series called The Lost Years of Merlin with the first book being called &quot;The Lost Years.&quot;<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">The Seven Songs of Merlin is the second book in a series called The Lost Years of Merlin with the first book being called "The Lost Years."<a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
</span>
