<span id="freeTextContainer10150215961811874083">I&apos;d forgotten until I was well into this that I&apos;d read it before. Probably because it&apos;s utterly forgettable. There are some really lovely descriptive passages and pretty writing, but I have zero connection to any of the characters. I couldn&apos;t wait to get to get to the end, and I&apos;ve already forgotten most of it. I didn&apos;t read the first one of the series or any that came after, nor shall I. This is going into the donate pile. Next!</span>
